==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

#[[Fact]]s or [[observation]]s presented in support of an [[assertion]].
#{{cattag|legal}} Anything admitted by a [[court]] to prove or disprove alleged matters of fact in a [[trial]].

